Title: Deutsches Nachrichtenbüro
Description.abstract: An internal serial publication of the German News Agency (Deutsches Nachrichtenbüro) before and during the Second World War. Published three or more times a day, UCLA holdings cover the period May 8 1936 to May 25, 1940. Digitization is under way and the digital copies will be published as completed.
